Vaagdevi Degree and P.G. College is one of the oldest and prestigious educational institutes in Telangana State, catering to the higher educational needs of this backward region. It was established in 1993 by Viswambhara Educational Society and affiliated to Kakatiya University. The College is managed by eminent educationists and social workers who are dedicated to the cause of imparting quality and value based education to the needy people of this region. Over the years, the College has earned reputation of imparting high quality education with holistic approach of developing overall personality of students.
Vaagdevi College of engineering (MCA) is promoted by Vishwanbara Educational Society, approved by the All India Council for Technical Education, Ministry of Human Resource Development, Govt.of India, New Delhi, vaagdevi college of engineering (MCA)started functioning from 1998. Located in Bollikunta, and 12 KM away from Warangal Railway station, Vaagdevicollege of engineering MCA has an enviable environment – serene, spacious and stupendous. It offers an ideal environment for imparting value- based Techno and management education.
